Gradecraft is a gamified gradebook. 

Current features: 
- Badges
- Teams (course-long memberships)
- Groups (single-assignment memberships)
- Assignments
- Assignment Types
- Student Dashboard 
- Grade Predictor
- Grading schemes
- Export students and final grades
- User analytics
- Team analytics
- Assignment stats

Upcoming:
- Automated attendance logging & scoring
- Omniauth
- Interactive rubrics
- Unified Gradebook view
- Interactive grading schemes (students select percentages for specified assignments)